#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
#include <map>
#include <vector>
#include <string>
#include <sstream>

using namespace std;

string v[] = {"JAN", "FEB", "MAR", "APR", "MAY", "JUN", "JUL", "AUG", "SEP", "OCT", "NOV", "DEC" };

int mm[] = { 0, 31, 28, 31, 30, 31, 30, 31, 31, 30, 31, 30 }; 

int main()
{
	int n;
	cin >> n;
	string s;
	string s1, s2, s3;
	int month, year, day, td = 0;
	

	for ( int cs = 1; cs <= n; cs++ )  {

		td = 0;
		stringstream ss1, ss2, ss3;

		cin >> s;

		s1 = s.substr ( 0, 2 );
		s2 = s.substr ( 3, 3 );
		s3 = s.substr ( 7, 4 );
//		ss1.clear();	ss3.clear();
//		ss1 = "";	ss3 = "";
		ss1 << s1;	ss1 >> day;
		ss3 << s3;	ss3 >> year;
		
		for ( int i = 0; i < 12; i++ ) {
			if ( v[i] == s2 ) month = i;
		}

		for ( int i = 0; i <= month; i++ ) 
			td += mm[i];
		
		td += day;
//		cout << td << endl;
		if ( year%400 == 0 || ( year%4 == 0 && year%100 != 0 ) ){
			if ( month > 1 ) 
				td++;
		}
			
		
		cout << "Case " << cs << ": ";
		if ( td <= 300 ) {
			cout << td << " Hundreds" << endl;
		}

		if ( td > 300 && td <= 360 ) {
			td -= 300;
			cout << td << " Tens" << endl;
		}			
		
		if ( td > 360 ) {
			td -= 360;
			cout << td << " Ones" << endl;
		}

	}

	return 0;
}
